attributes.action: Denmark Street, Soho is an historic place for music in our country. It MUST NOT be demolished
attributes.additional_details: Denmark Street in London's Soho has long been associated with many famous bands from around the world. To demolish this street would be criminal. Some of the buildings are listed properties so what about the ruling on that! I don't think the Culture Secretary is even aware of what's going on.

rejection.details: This is a matter for the Council.  The listed buildings are not under threat.
